### [Mobile] Video Format Support
#### [INSTALL] Dependencies
- `npm install @ffmpeg/ffmpeg @ffmpeg/util` for client-side transcoding of `.mov` (HEVC) to [.mp4](file:///C:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/Videos/Cod%20Mastery%20Gaming%20Short%2000125.mp4) (H.264).
#### [MODIFY] [app/upload/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/upload/page.tsx)
- Integrate `ffmpeg.wasm` to transcode mobile formats before upload.
- Expand `ALLOWED_VIDEO_TYPES` to include `video/quicktime`, `video/hevc`, and `video/mp4`.
- **Category Selection**: Add `CATEGORY_LIST` (Gaming, Music, Tech, Entertainment, News, Sports).
- **Auto-Thumbnails**: 
    - Use a hidden `<video>` element and `<canvas>` to capture 3 stills at 20%, 50%, and 80% marks.
    - Display these as clickable cards alongside the "Custom Upload" option.
    - Allow user to toggle between "Auto" and "Custom" thumbnail source.

### [Mobile] Responsiveness Overhaul
#### [MODIFY] [components/Navbar.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/Navbar.tsx)
- Implement a cleaner mobile search (icon-only until clicked).
- Use `flex-wrap` and `overflow-x-hidden` protection.
#### [MODIFY] [components/Sidebar.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/Sidebar.tsx)
- Ensure the sidebar behaves as an overlay on mobile instead of pushing content.
- Increase tap targets for icons.

### [Bugfix] Upload restoration
#### [INVESTIGATE] [app/api/upload/route.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/app/api/upload/route.ts) & [app/upload/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/upload/page.tsx)
- Check for R2 configuration errors or CORS issues.
- Verify presigned URL generation and the subsequent PUT request.
#### [INVESTIGATE] Manual CORS Verification
- The automated script failed with AccessDenied. I will provide the exact CORS JSON configuration for the user to paste into the Cloudflare R2 dashboard.
- CORS Configuration (JSON):
```json
[
  {
    "AllowedHeaders": ["*"],
    "AllowedMethods": ["GET", "PUT", "POST", "DELETE", "HEAD"],
    "AllowedOrigins": ["*"],
    "ExposeHeaders": ["ETag"],
    "MaxAgeSeconds": 3000
  }
]
```

### [UI] Channel (Profile) Page Rebuild
#### [MODIFY] [app/profile/[username]/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/.gemini/antigravity/playground/sonic-zenith/app/profile/%5Busername%5D/page.tsx)
